THAI TRADE CENTRES AROUND THE WORLD
There are 18 Thai Trade Centres in cities around the world. They
provide regularly updated trading contacts, matched to specific product
needs; details of Thai trade fairs and information for individual
business itineraries, plus hotel reservations at competitive prices in
Thailand.
In the UK, the Thai Trade Centre is located at Elizabeth House (3rd
floor), St Peter's Square, Manchester M2 3DF. Tel 44 (0) 61 236 0445;
fax 44 (0) 61 236 0347.
Other Thai trade centres in Europe are located at Frankfurt tel 49 69
281 091; Milan, tel 39 2 669 81756; Rotterdam, tel 31 10 415 8663. The
UK centre (see above) has details of all other European offices.
Centres in Japan are based at Osaka, tel 81 6 262 4418 and in Fukuoka,
tel 81 92 751 6311. Other international centres are located in New
York, tel 1 212 466 1777; Vancouver, tel 1 604 687 6400; and Sydney,
tel 61 2 241 1075.
